rsection\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was then opened and the torch handed to Thierry Henry, one of the greats of French football.\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 903, \"end\": 916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thierry Henry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the torch\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 892}, {\"ngram\": \"the greats\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"French football\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As cheers rose from the crowd, Henry set off at a slow jog, bearing the now-lit torch towards the nearby Place de la Concorde.\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 1083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1062, \"end\": 1082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7917278555011027e-31, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cheers\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"Henry\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 993}, {\"ngram\": \"a slow jog\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"the now-lit torch\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is closed, like much of Paris, to accommodate Olympic events.\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1111, \"end\": 1116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2594559845082104e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_ph